  "_comment": "Recorded NetBox 4.6-shaped REST read responses (issue #36 test fixtures). Keys are the relative endpoint paths the importer pulls; each value is the de-paginated 'results' list. FKs serialize as brief {id,url,display,name,slug,...}; choice fields (status/role/family) as {value,label}; prefixes/VLANs carry the 4.2+ scope_type/scope_id/scope shape. This single install models: 2 VRFs (cust-a / cust-b) with the SAME 10.50.0.0/24 prefix in each (overlap that must coexist in 2 spaces), 1 tenant (Acme) -> Customer, a region->site tree, an aggregate, a container/leaf/enclosing-active prefix mix, a multicast prefix, VLANs (incl. a vid clash + a name clash), and addresses.",
